INSERT INTO `posts` (`author`, `title`, `description`, `url`, `source`, `image`, `category`, `published_at`) VALUES ('Katharina Buczek', 'Her Stepmother Gave Her Money To Buy Her Perfect Wedding Dress But Then Asked Her To Wear A Hand-Me-Down Gown From The 1970s Instead Because Her Stepsister Is Insecure', 'This 23-year-old woman recently celebrated an exciting milestone– she just got engaged! INSERT INTO `posts` (`author`, `title`, `description`, `url`, `source`, `image`, `category`, `published_at`) VALUES ('Petty Officer 1st Class April Enos', 'U.S. Navy Band Celebrates Black History Month on Good Morning Washington', 'Celebrating Black History Month, Chief Musician Nathaniel Wilson, from Lake Ann, Mich., and Chief Musician Joshua Arvizu, from DeRidder La., join the hosts of ABC\'s Good Morning Washington to discuss the premier of the Alton Augustus Adam Sr. Award for Emerging Composers, created to honor the legacy of the Navy\'s first Black bandmaster. The inagural award\'s first winner, Jaylin Vinson, from Oklahoma City, Ok., will join the Navy Band Woodwind Quintet to hear the premier of his piece \"Afrophilia\" at Howard University on Feb. 9, 2023.', 'https://www.dvidshub.net/image/7624115/us-navy-band-celebrates-black-history-month-good-morning-washington', 'dvidshub', 'https://cdn.dvidshub.net/media/thumbs/photos/2302/7624115/250x166_q75.jpg', 'general', '2023-02-09T02:03:06+00:00')
